   <talk_paragraph index="n013_cleric_tomas-3" image="QN_SoceressCynthia.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_question mid="11"><![CDATA[<html>$Cleric Thomas${action:Talk}<BR>There's a door? You're certain?<BR>Hmm... If so, we must find out where the door leads to.<BR><FONT color=#a82424>Master Sorceress Cynthia</FONT> should know more, since she lives here.<BR>Go and ask her. Be nice.</html>]]></talk_question>
