      <talk_question mid="12"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>You found the <FONT color=#a82424>Dragon Follower</FONT> in <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT>? How did he ...<BR>There's no way out of that place. Why is he there?</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-3-a" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-3-b" mid="15"><![CDATA[<html>Where in Marian's Shrine does the door lead to?</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="14"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia${action:Talk}<BR>Yes... the door! The wooden door constructed that leads to <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT> from <FONT color=#a82424>Frost Wind Forest</FONT>. I'm amazed that the door is still around ...<BR>and he even managed to find it.</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
   <talk_paragraph index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-3-b" image="QW_11.dds" itemindex="">
      <talk_answer link_index="n012_sorceress_master_cynthia-3-c" mid="17"><![CDATA[<html>Okay.</html>]]></talk_answer>
      <talk_question mid="16"><![CDATA[<html>$Master Sorceress Cynthia$<BR>Through the door, you will reach the lowest level of <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT>. It's a long and narrow passage that hasn't been used for a long time. Be extra careful.<BR>Go to <FONT color=#a82424>Marian's Shrine</FONT> right away. Before you lose him for good!</html>]]></talk_question>
   </talk_paragraph>
